{"tid":656579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葛珮帆第3度收恐嚇信　紙黏死曱甴嚇煞職員","createTime":"2018-05-07T10:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:19:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e242074d05e2806b2e7f802c54127b2aee2ebf79","tid":656579,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/photo/bkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180507%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001_01p.jpg&d=N2JbAIWa9%2FbI8JrruRbENh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=919f2ad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/photo/bkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001_01p.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n恐嚇信紙上黏着多隻蟑螂屍體。(葛珮帆提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/photo/bkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180507185235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180507%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180507185235&h=3a53f206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆又再收到恐嚇信。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆早前兩度收到死亡恐嚇信後，今日(7日)再度收到恐嚇信。是次的恐嚇信並無任何文字，只有2張黏上多隻蟑螂屍體的紙張，而那些蟑螂屍體亦已被壓扁。葛珮帆的議員辦事處職員已就事件報案。<br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆表示，負責拆開該封恐嚇信的女職員被信件嚇至大聲尖叫和跳開，並感到十分驚慌，認為是死亡恐嚇。對於發信者的行為，她認為極其幼稚和無聊，又指該行為已涉嫌觸犯刑事罪行。她表示，香港是法治社會，任何人不應以恐嚇他人的方式表達意見，又指任何形式的恐嚇行為均為嚴重罪行，必須予以正視，不能姑息。<br />\n<br />\n於2016年立法會換屆選舉後，多名民主派議員因宣誓風波而遭取消議員資格(DQ)，引發早前的立法會補選，但最終有多名民主自決派人士參選，被當區選舉主任取消參選資格。律政司司長鄭若驊、2名選舉主任及多名立法會議員於3月份接連收到來自日本的恐嚇信，稱要殺死鄭和2名選舉主任。<br />\n<br />\n繼收到來自日本的恐嚇信，葛珮帆於上月再收到由香港寄出的死亡恐嚇信，寄信人在信中用大字寫上「你會死！」文中更稱會暗殺你，並指會監視葛的一舉一動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/bkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180507%2Fbkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001.html&d=N2JbAIWa9%2FbI8JrruRbENh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=36cfd234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/bkn-20180507181627483-0507_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d8d0e5271dd2ede6bf69f2d0586ce8c20bcf49d4","tid":656579,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f29daa545b1f49022a3115b92a397970f0f633","tid":656579,"uid":113626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港驚條鐵咩, 日本就話真係多痴線佬會郁手"},{"pid":"a93a0124d1aef8079f255be059d4639a66d778c1","tid":656579,"uid":60287,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"唔係做咁多陰質野點會覺得兩隻蟲仔就係死亡恐嚇"},{"pid":"08cf9c3c3690df743ef42a3ca02608e90d995489","tid":656579,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"你會死!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢句嘢有恐嚇成份咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢長生不老㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會殺死你，先算恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e71b7f3a7814615e4218755c6cddc76606a7f6","tid":656579,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"你會死都算係恐嚇？<br />\n人地只係講個事實出嚟咋喎&hellip;唔只佢，係人都會死架啦"},{"pid":"00120afc6237fe6df09b77e6a8c1f2178d53b2a6","tid":656579,"uid":82532,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070523/large/23lp2p21new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070523%2Flarge%2F23lp2p21new.jpg&h=0b811874&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad1e1b7a8560d4f37acd1bf26251deb5